&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About NewLimit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NewLimit is a biotechnology company working to radically extend human healthspan. We’re developing medicines to treat aging by reprogramming the epigenome, a new therapeutic mechanism to restore youthful function in aged cells. We’ve built the world’s leading experimental and artificial intelligence system to discover reprogramming medicines at massive scale. Our first products are focused on restoring youthful metabolic, endothelial, and immune function.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NewLimit is seeking an executive assistant to provide administrative support to the CEO and executive team.&amp;nbsp; This role will be fast-paced and provide you the rare opportunity to help build and scale a leading technology company. You’ll have the opportunity to support the CEO &amp;amp; executive team across all areas of the business, learning what’s required to grow a company in a deep scientific domain.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a member of our team, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage administrative responsibilities for the CEO &amp;amp; executive team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the communication switchboard for our executives, ensuring the right information arrives at the right place &amp;amp; time is prioritized effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with our Finance and Legal teams to solve problems, maintain accurate records, and liaise with external parties&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support our executive team on business development, fundraising, and scientific projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan events large and small, including our annual progress updates and corporate off-sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;≥5 years of experience in a similar executive support role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in a relevant field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;History of completing meaningful projects given high-level direction (e.g. event planning, fundraising processes, office management)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing complex calendars&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;History of producing high-quality work products in the form of documents, slides, and spreadsheets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a high-growth startup environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Notion, Google Workspace, Greenhouse, or Rippling systems is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in the tech or biotech sector&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience supporting teams across HR, Operations, Talent, or others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Compensation for the role will depend on a number of factors, including a candidate’s qualifications, skills, competencies, and experience. NewLimit offers a competitive benefits package, which includes a 401k, healthcare coverage, and 20 days of PTO. Learn more at:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.newlimit.com/careers&quot;&gt;https://www.newlimit.com/careers&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; *This compensation and benefits information is based on Company&#39;s good faith estimate as of the date of publication and may be modified in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;About NewLimit&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NewLimit is a biotechnology company working to radically extend human healthspan. We’re developing medicines to treat age-related diseases by reprogramming the epigenome, a new therapeutic mechanism to restore regenerative potential in aged and diseased cells. We leverage functional genomics, pooled perturbation screening, and machine learning models to unravel the biology of epigenetic aging and disease using experiments of unprecedented scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Position&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NewLimit is seeking an Executive Recruiter to own all executive-level hiring for our fast-growing company. NewLimit is a science-driven organization operating at the confluence of multiple highly-technical fields. For many of our executive roles, there are fewer than 100 qualified candidates in the world. This is an opportunity to partner directly with our executive team, navigate highly specialized talent pools, and help build the leadership bench that will scale the company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of your role, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with our executive team and senior leadership to scope executive-level positions, define success criteria, and develop hiring strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Source and recruit executive talent across technical, operational, and commercial domains — identifying rare candidates who combine deep domain expertise with leadership caliber&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end recruiting process for all executive hires: from sourcing and candidate development through offer negotiation and close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop relationships with top-tier talent across computational biology, machine learning, functional genomics, immunology, and related fields&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute with excellence across all unit operations (sourcing, scheduling, closing) to deliver high-impact hires&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to scaling recruiting processes and strategies to support accelerating hiring needs across the organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Requirements&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-year experience recruiting at the executive level (VP+, C-suite) in top-tier biotechnology or technology companies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success sourcing and closing rare, highly specialized talent, ideally with a track record of recruiting candidates from exceptionally narrow talent pools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience executing end-to-end recruiting cycles for executive-level roles with strong attention to candidate experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic partnership skills: ability to collaborate with C-suite and senior leaders to understand business needs, define roles, and build alignment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communicator who can articulate company vision and culture compellingly to senior executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
