&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree or greater in natural sciences or engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience recruiting within computational biology, machine learning, cell &amp;amp; molecular biology, functional genomics, or immunology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background working with early-to-growth-stage companies navigating rapid scaling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building or improving recruiting function strategy and processes&lt;/li&gt;
