&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with our Functional Genomics and Predictive Modeling teams to test reprogramming hypotheses at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure the impact of mRNA reprogramming medicines on endothelial cell function&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engineer &lt;em&gt;in vivo&lt;/em&gt; nucleic acid delivery methods for endothelial cells&lt;/li&gt;
