&lt;li&gt;Experience with primary cell isolation and functional characterization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with mouse models (e.g. kidney, cardiovascular, or cognitive disease models)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with transgenic manipulation of primary cells either &lt;em&gt;ex vivo&lt;/em&gt; &lt;strong&gt;or&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;in vivo&lt;/em&gt; (e.g. using viral vectors, nucleic acid delivery)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
