&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;History of contributing to a drug development program at the pre-clinical or clinical development stage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading the design and execution of pre-clinical studies in mouse models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with single cell genomics methods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with pooled screening approaches using bulk or single cell read-outs (e.g. CRISPR fitness screens, Perturb/CROP-seq)&lt;/li&gt;
